narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The class is a great survey of Mediterranean history in the 20th century. By learning about the dictatorships in countries such as Spain, Greece and Yugoslavia, you develop a much better understanding of South European history.Prof. Maragkou is a great professor, the reading workload is manageable and class discussion is intellectually stimulating.
Good class. You will learn a lot about the specific dictatorships as well as the theory of dictatorship.
